title: Dark Souls II Scholar of the First Sin PS3-DUPLEX
description:
Summary:

The undead curse continues to spread across the kingdom of Drangleic with Dark Souls II: Scholar of the First Sin, a compilation of the critically acclaimed Dark Souls II with its three DLC chapters (Crown Of The Sunken King, Crown Of The Old Iron King, and Crown Of The Ivory King) along with an array of all-new content. This edition of Dark Souls II: Scholar of the First Sin takes advantage of the power of new-generation platforms with enhanced graphics in addition to brand new game content, including an expanded story featuring additional in-game events and NPC character along with new deadlier enemies and gameplay improvements.
